<style>
  :host {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 400px;
    max-width: 1200px;
  }

  .desktop, .mobile {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  [if] {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  @media(min-width: 1200px) {
    :host {
      flex-direction: row;
      width: 80%;
    }
  }
</style>
<slot name="left"></slot>
<slot name="right"></slot>
